Air Jordan 35 GS 'Bred'
results.story: Made for grade schoolers, the Air Jordan 35 GS ‘Bred’ dresses the performance hoops shoe in a color scheme baked into the DNA of the Jordan franchise. The black finish of the suede and mesh upper is contrasted by a silver reflective tongue that recalls the Air Jordan 5, complete with a Jumpman icon in Fire Red. Additional flecks of crimson land on the Flightwire cables that reinforce the sneaker’s side panels. A color-fade effect in black and red is applied to the Eclipse Plate, with the latter hue seeping into the herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: Air Force 1 GS 'Recycled Wool Pack - Black'
results.story: Made for grade schoolers, the Nike Air Force 1 GS ‘Black’ is drawn from the ‘Recycled Wool Pack,’ featuring an assortment of retro silhouettes incorporating sustainable materials. This pair carries a blacked-out synthetic leather upper made with 25% recycled fibers, accented with 100% recycled felt on the tongue and heel tab. Encapsulated Air cushioning enhances the speckled cupsole, featuring 15% Nike Grind made with left-over rubber scraps from the sneaker manufacturing process.

results.name: Air VaporMax 2020 GS 'Light Bone'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Nike Air VaporMax 2020 GS ‘Light Bone’ adds bright accents to a lifestyle runner built with sustainability in mind. Recycled polyester is integrated into the Flyknit upper, rendered in subdued tan hues that are contrasted by a marbled TPU heel counter in a bright yellow finish. Dual pull tabs provide easy on and off, while a FlyEase lacing system uses quick-pull straps for quick adjustments on the go. A low-profile VaporMax unit delivers lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Kylian Mbappé x LeBron 18 GS NRG 'The Chosen 2'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Kylian Mbappé x Nike LeBron 18 GS NRG ‘The Chosen 2’ brings together two iconic athletes who embody the competitive spirit of their respective sports. The sneaker’s black knit upper is accented with embroidered red Swooshes and a metallic iridescent tongue, the latter featuring decorative Air pods with mismatched LeBron and Kylian branding. A functional Max Air unit provides lightweight cushioning under the heel, nestled below a semi-translucent heel clip and supported by a semi-translucent rubber outsole, both of which are finished in a swirling blend of violet and blue tones.

results.name: Star Runner 2 PS 'Thunder Blue Purple Pulse'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Star Runner 2 PS ‘Thunder Blue Purple Pulse’ offers a simplistic two-tone colorway of the casual running shoe. A navy mesh and synthetic leather upper is accented with a pale violet Swoosh and secured with an adjustable hook-and-loop strap and elastic no-tie laces. The lightweight build rides on a contrasting white foam midsole, supported by durable rubber in high-wear areas. ‘Run Fast’ is inscribed under the heel as a reminder to keep little feet moving.

results.name: Air Force 1 GS 'Recycled Wool Pack - White'
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the Nike Air Force 1 GS ‘White’ is drawn from the ‘Recycled Wool Pack,’ featuring assorted classic silhouettes made with Earth-friendly materials. The iconic low-top showcases a monochrome white upper made with synthetic leather that includes at least 25% recycled fibers. Laces are made with 20% recycled polyester, while the felted material on the tongue and heel tab feature 100% recycled content. The unique look of the speckled cupsole indicates the usage of Nike Grind, incorporating rubber scraps that are the byproduct of sneaker manufacturing.

results.name: Air Force 1 PS 'Recycled Wool Pack - Black'
results.story: Developed for little kids, the Nike Air Force 1 PS ‘Black’ is one of the classic silhouettes that make up the ‘Recycled Wool Pack,’ comprising a variety of classic silhouettes built with sustainability in mind. The black synthetic leather upper on this pair uses 25% recycled fibers, while 100% recycled felt makes up the composition of the marled tongue tag and heel tab. A speckled finish distinguishes a durable cupsole partially made with Nike Grind, featuring leftover scrap rubber collected from factory floors.

results.name: Air Force 1 PS 'Recycled Wool Pack - White'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Air Force 1 PS ‘White’ is included in the ‘Recycled Wool Pack,’ comprising classic silhouettes built with sustainable materials. The synthetic leather upper on this pair incorporates at least 25% recycled fibers, while the felted textile used on the tongue and heel tab is made with 100% recycled content. The low-top rides on a speckled cupsole made with approximately 15% Nike Grind, a compound made with rubber scraps produced during sneaker manufacturing.

results.name: Air Max Excee PS 'Black Blue Void'
results.story: Made for little kids, the Nike Air Max Excee PS ‘Black Blue Void’ features a familiar design that takes inspiration from the classic Air Max 90. The upper combines black mesh with navy leather overlays and a black suede quarter panel embellished with contrast zigzag stitching. A floating leather Swoosh stands out in a vibrant Signal Blue finish. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a foam midsole, enhanced with a visible Max Air unit in the heel.

Court Legacy PS 'White Sunset Pulse'
results.story: The Nike Court Legacy PS ‘White Sunset Pulse’ highlights pastel accents on a tennis-inspired sneaker built for little kids. A crisp white leather upper is secured with an adjustable hook-and-loop strap and elastic no-tie laces. The signature Swoosh is finished in a bright pink hue, matching a Nike wordmark on the heel tab and pinstripe detailing on the midsole. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a classic herringbone traction pattern for optimal grip.

Wearallday GS 'Signal Blue'
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the Nike Wearallday GS ‘Signal Blue’ applies aqueous hues to a minimalist mesh upper, bolstered with synthetic no-sew overlays at the toe and heel for enhanced durability. A padded collar provides a comfortable fit, while a webbing pull tab at the heel delivers easy on and off. The sleek low-top is mounted on a bulky foam midsole, supported by a full-length rubber outsole for sure footing.

results.name: Wearallday PS 'Midnight Navy Volt'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Wearallday PS ‘Midnight Navy Volt’ showcases fluorescent accents on a lightweight, versatile sneaker. A combination of no-tie elastic laces and an adjustable hook-and-loop strap secures the navy mesh upper, reinforced with no-sew overlays in Baltic Blue. A webbing pull tab at the heel is rendered in Volt, matching the signature Swoosh and Nike branding atop the midfoot strap. Plush cushioning arrives via a bulky foam midsole in a crisp white finish.

results.name: Jordan Why Not Zer0.4 GS 'Upbringing'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Jordan Why Not Zer0.4 GS ‘Upbringing' features mismatched prints and colors on the upper of the left and right shoe, resulting in a kaleidoscopic design that takes inspiration from Russell Westbrook’s formative years in Southern California. The complex build combines breathable mesh with lightweight textile, synthetic overlays and cracked leather paneling on the heel. Zoom Air cushioning is housed in the heel of the foam midsole, supported by a decoupled translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Wearallday GS 'Glacier Blue'
results.story: A versatile sneaker offered in grade school sizing, the Nike Wearallday GS ‘Glacier Blue’ lives up to its descriptive moniker with a lightweight build that delivers lasting comfort. A crisp white finish distinguishes the breathable textile upper, equipped with a black webbing pull tab and accented with seamless icy blue overlays at the toe and heel. Plush cushioning comes courtesy of a soft foam midsole, reinforced by a durable full-length rubber outsole.

results.name: Team Hustle D9 FlyEase GS 'Black High Voltage'
results.story: Developed for big kids, the Nike Team Hustle D9 FlyEase GS ‘Black High Voltage’ features easy entry technology on an everyday sneaker dressed in a simple two-tone color scheme. The mid-top makes use of a breathable black mesh upper, secured with the combination of a hook-and-loop strap and a zipper that wraps around the heel, allowing the shoe to be easily taken on and off. A soft foam midsole is reinforced with a rubber outsole that wraps up the sidewalls for added durability.

results.name: Court Legacy GS 'White Sunset Pulse'
results.story: Developed for grade schoolers, the Nike Court Legacy GS ‘White Sunset Pulse’ applies pastel accents to a casual sneaker that takes its design cues from classic tennis shoes of the ‘70s and ‘80s. A pink Swoosh is stitched onto the clean white leather upper, matching the Nike wordmark emblazoned across the heel tab. Foam cushioning provides step-in comfort, while a herringbone traction pattern delivers maximum grip underfoot.

Air Max Excee PS 'White Arctic Punch'
results.story: Developed for little kids, the Nike Air Max Excee PS ‘White Arctic Punch’ enlivens the Air Max 90-inspired silhouette with candy-bright accents. The sneaker’s white mesh upper is bolstered with tonal leather overlays and a bright pink leather mudguard. An iridescent finish shines on the Nike branded heel patch, while the Swoosh is rendered in gradient pink, grey and yellow tones. A visible Max Air unit is nestled in the heel of the foam midsole, supported by a waffle traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Star Runner 2 PS 'Smoke Grey'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Star Runner 2 PS ‘Smoke Grey’ delivers a mostly neutral colorway of a versatile sneaker ready made for play. No-tie elastic laces and an adjustable hook-and-loop strap secure an upper constructed from mesh and synthetic leather. The neutral grey finish is contrasted by a white Swoosh and unexpected pink hits on the tongue tag and collar lining. Lightweight cushioning arrives via soft foam midsole, supported underfoot by durable rubber in high-wear areas.

Flex Runner PS 'Game Royal'
results.story: Developed for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Game Royal’ showcases varying blue shades on a convenient slip-on build constructed from stretchy textile and mesh. Dual webbing pull tabs provide easy on and off, while a synthetic leather overlay offers added durability and support. The monochrome color palette up top is offset by a stark white foam sole unit, its underside etched with flex grooves that promote the foot’s natural stride.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Camo'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Camo’ applies a vibrant palette to a comfortable slip-on sneaker engineered for play. The breathable textile and mesh upper is rendered in Active Fuchsia, an eye-catching hue that’s repeated on the camo-print synthetic leather overlay. The multicolor array up top is countered by a solid white foam sole, equipped with flex grooves that allow feet to move and bend naturally.

results.story: Developed for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Atomic Pink’ updates the slip-on silhouette with a simplistic two-tone color scheme. The pastel hue that floods the mesh and textile upper is contrasted by a slate blue synthetic leather overlay, secured with elastic straps that wrap over the midfoot and around the heel. The lightweight build is supported by a soft foam sole unit, featuring multiple flex grooves that accommodate the natural movement of the foot.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Pink Glow'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Pink Glow’ delivers a comfortable and versatile sneaker with no laces needed. A monochrome black finish is applied to the stretchy textile and mesh upper, equipped with pink webbing pull tabs that assist in easy on and off. Added durability and support are provided by a synthetic leather overlay in a dark pink hue. The slip-on rides on a soft foam midsole, featuring flex grooves that accommodate the foot’s natural movement.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Light Smoke Grey Total Orange'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Light Smoke Grey Total Orange’ makes use of a convenient slip-on build, free of laces and equipped with pull tabs at the tongue and heel for easy on and off. A neutral grey finish is applied to the stretchy upper, constructed from a blend of fabric and mesh. A black synthetic leather overlay provides added support and durability. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a white foam sole unit, featuring flex grooves that promote a natural stride.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Fable'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Fable’ draws inspiration from Aesop’s moral about the tortoise and hare. Each character’s likeness is represented on the sneaker’s mismatched pink and blue pull tabs, which provide easy on and off for the laceless silhouette. The upper, constructed from black mesh and textile, is reinforced with synthetic leather overlays covered in a multicolor kaleidoscopic print. Integrated into the vibrant florals are depictions of the tortoise and hare in mid stride.
